    <description>Package Description</description>
    <releaseNotes>'Merged PR 11132: Fixed EndOfFlowValidate test method where when there's no other DFF failures, it will miss DNS handling'
'Merged PR 10200:  New set of API to search for tokens within VID level. New param for PrimeGetDffTestMethod to utilize new API behavior.'
'Merged PR 10080: [HDBI][PrimeDffFooterPrintTestMethod] Capability to print MTL into ITUFF'
'Merged PR 9500: Adding Feature VID verifaction to DffService'
'Merged PR 8343: Cleaning up .net analyzer's issues.'
'Merged PR 8326: More Roslyn's clean up.'
'Merged PR 7876: TOS4 sync to the master (ww01)'</releaseNotes>
